<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-122] remove &quot;style=&apos;bold&apos;&quot; in-line style declarations.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-122</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;During conversion, a bunch of &apos;style=bold&apos; in-line declarations were created particularly on the &amp;lt;emphasis&amp;gt; elements. These should be removed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Style instructions should note be included in the docbook xml.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="17526">LUDOC-122</key>
            <summary>remove &quot;style=&apos;bold&apos;&quot; in-line style declarations.</summary>
